(951, 'ACS (ARIES CCD spectrograph)', 1, '', 'optical, ', 0.000000, 1, 0.000000, 1, '', '', '', '', 0, '1024 x 1024', 0, 0, 0, 'Tektronics 1k CCD with 24 micron pixel size', 'This HR-320 spectrograph is used with the Tek 1k CCD detector to take low resolution spectra of bright stars up to 12 mag. It uses circular aperture and is best suited for estimating continuum and broad (EW 10 angstrom or higher) emission features in stars or astronomical objects.'),
