(24, 'Venus Express', 2, NULL, '2005-11-09', '2014-12-31', 'http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Venus_Express/', 'Venus Express is a satellite optimised for studying the atmosphere of Venus, from the surface right up to the ionosphere. It has been successfully operating in orbit around Venus since April 2006.\r\n\r\nSee also: http://sci.esa.int/science-e/www/area/index.cfm?fareaid=64', '2011-03-04 10:25:27', '2012-07-19 15:15:53', NULL, NULL),
